{"tid":1255802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家保持冷靜 626晚會仍然係重點","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T01:56:41.000Z","uid":36134,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52c6beccbe1102602d7b17eaa368c4e045405f1c","tid":1255802,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"627 野餐<br />\n至於其他行動 我覺得已經有d失控<br />\n時間太倉促 <br />\n為左一時之氣 咁短時間之內要升級行動<br />\n宣傳又唔夠時間<br />\n對之後整個運動帶黎既混亂<br />\n我真係難以形容<br />\n624教訓仲唔夠？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示威唔係示弱<br />\n唔係靠股蠻力就可以<br />\n成件事太急太無部署 好難班到足夠既人<br />\n我會遵從一開始既plan<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知道會比人屌我係鬼<br />\n但我都要講 根本成個運動部署越黎越急<br />\n越黎越亂<br />\n但我覺得我地需要冷靜d<br />\n急對成件事無好處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出席626晚會 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出席626全日活動"},{"pid":"8c9172c80957916e73ab5abad397b244c6ac3e33","tid":1255802,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b239c6acb3afeb5f42ebbd3cc82cef7656c8f15","tid":1255802,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f86ecf0b171a64a99ff032e20f4f7cc410b89c6","tid":1255802,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"正皮既幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ca61022fe4235aa1ebd47f6aa2711dab629845","tid":1255802,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T00:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b1fda8c51045fe47607b03cbaf2438e3d91fbb0","tid":1255802,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:08:28.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，<br />\n<br />\n之前有個post話G20果日係各國報紙登關於反送中既頭版廣告（<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1252292/page/1），好多人都贊成，但